<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{خَلَاقٍ}</span> ... نَصِيبٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{رَاعِنَا}</span> ... كَلِمَةٌ كَانَ الْيَهُودُ يَقُولُونَهَا لِلنَّبِيِّ - صلى الله عليه وسلم - بِقَصْدِ السَّبِّ، وَنِسْبَتِهِ إِلَى الرُّعونَةِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٠٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{انظُرْنَا}</span> ... انْظُرْ إِلَيْنَا، وَتَعَهَّدْنَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
